    question:
      'How does the writer use language to create a sense of danger in the extract below?\n\n"The wind screamed through the broken shutters, hurling shards of ice against the walls. Each gust carried with it the acrid stench of smoke and something else — something ancient and predatory. The shadows in the hallway seemed to breathe, expanding and contracting like the ribs of some vast, slumbering beast. Maria pressed her back against the door, her fingers white-knuckled around the handle, and listened to the silence that was somehow worse than any sound."',
